                        <p>Get captions generated in under 60 seconds no learning curve required.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="steps-grid">
                        <div class="step-card" data-step="1">
                            <div class="step-number">01</div>
                            <div class="step-icon">
                                <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
                                    <rect width="40" height="40" rx="12" fill="url(#sg1)" />
                                    <path d="M13 20h14M20 13l7 7-7 7" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2"
                                        stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                                    <defs>
                                        <linearGradient id="sg1" x1="0" y1="0" x2="40" y2="40">
                                            <stop stop-color="#6A00FF" />
                                            <stop offset="1" stop-color="#A259FF" />
                                        </linearGradient>
                                    </defs>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3>Install Qwint Caption Plugin</h3>
                            <p>Download and install the plugin from our website in one click. Compatible with Premiere
                                Pro 2022
                                and above.</p>
                            <div class="step-connector"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-card" data-step="2">
                            <div class="step-number">02</div>
                            <div class="step-icon">
                                <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
                                    <rect width="40" height="40" rx="12" fill="url(#sg2)" />
                                    <rect x="11" y="15" width="18" height="12" rx="3" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" />
                                    <path d="M17 20l4 2.5 4-2.5" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5"
                                        stroke-linecap="round" />
                                    <defs>
                                        <linearGradient id="sg2" x1="0" y1="0" x2="40" y2="40">
                                            <stop stop-color="#6A00FF" />
                                            <stop offset="1" stop-color="#A259FF" />
                                        </linearGradient>
                                    </defs>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3>Open Premiere Pro &amp; Click Generate</h3>
                            <p>Open your project in Premiere Pro. Find Qwint Caption in the Extensions panel and click
                                "Generate
                                Captions".</p>
                            <div class="step-connector"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-card" data-step="3">
                            <div class="step-number">03</div>
                            <div class="step-icon">
                                <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
