            <!-- ===== FAQ ===== -->
            <section class="section faq" id="faq">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="section-header">
                        <span class="section-tag">Got Questions?</span>
                        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-list">
                        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                            <div class="faq-question">
                                <span>Does it work with Premiere Pro 2023 and 2024?</span>
                                <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>Yes! Qwint Caption is fully compatible with Adobe Premiere Pro 2022, 2023, and 2024
                                    (versions
                                    22.0 and above). We regularly update the plugin to support the latest Premiere Pro
                                    releases,
                                    so you'll always be covered.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                            <div class="faq-question">
                                <span>How accurate are the AI-generated captions?</span>
                                <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>Qwint Caption uses state-of-the-art AI transcription that achieves 95-98% word
                                    accuracy on
                                    clear audio. Accuracy depends on audio quality, background noise, and speaker
                                    clarity. We
                                    recommend recording in a quiet environment for best results. You can always
                                    fine-tune
                                    captions directly in Premiere Pro after generation.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                            <div class="faq-question">
                                <span>Which languages are supported?</span>
                                <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>We support 50+ languages including English, Hindi, Spanish, French, German,
                                    Portuguese,
                                    Japanese, Korean, Arabic, Tamil, Telugu, and many more. The plugin auto-detects the
                                    language
                                    spoken in your video, or you can manually select a language for best accuracy.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                            <div class="faq-question">
                                <span>How does the credit system work?</span>
                                <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>Credits are measured in minutes of video processed. For example, generating captions
                                    for a
                                    5-minute video uses 5 minutes of credits. You get 1 minute free on signup. Top-up
                                    checkout
                                    is being finalized, and credits will continue to be non-expiring.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
