                                <p>Qwint Caption places captions directly on your Premiere Pro timeline as editable text
                                    layers.
                                    You can also export as SRT (SubRip), VTT (WebVTT), or bake captions into your video
                                    during
                                    export whichever workflow suits you best.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                            <div class="faq-question">
                                <span>Is my video data secure?</span>
                                <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
